# pnpm hoisting configuration
# Storybook 9.x + pnpm strict isolation are incompatible: the builder-manager
# uses @yarnpkg/esbuild-plugin-pnp internally, which calls module.findPnpApi()
# and traverses up the directory tree looking for a .pnp.cjs file.
# A stale Yarn PnP artifact existed at ~/Desktop/projetos/.pnp.cjs and was
# removed manually. This hoisting config is kept as a safety net so @storybook
# packages are always resolvable from root node_modules regardless.
# Remove when @storybook-vue/nuxt supports Storybook 10+.
public-hoist-pattern[]=storybook
public-hoist-pattern[]=@storybook/*
